## Post 57: The Experiment Router

> A source lead is not a result.
>
> The next Telos layer is an experiment router: take a paper/source, demote noisy matches, and choose the smallest honest next packet.
>
> Quantum paper? Maybe a noise-model packet.
> Climate paper? Data/model/uncertainty packet.
> Proof paper? Replay packet.
>
> The goal is not "AI solved science." The goal is forcing every scientific claim to carry the receipt it deserves.

