## Post 59: Why Query Noise Matters

> Query noise is not just cleanup. It is product signal.
>
> If a climate search pulls media verification, or a proof search pulls governance, the system should not hide that. It should demote it, preserve it, and prevent accidental promotion.
>
> Scientific tools need visible negative controls.

