## Post 60: Formal Proof Is The Fastest Path To A Real Win

> In the frontier-science roadmap, formal proof is the nearest clean demo path.
>
> A theorem/proof-assistant source lead can become a replay packet:
>
> source -> environment -> command -> proof object -> verifier verdict.
>
> If replay fails, the result is still useful: an honest `UNVERIFIABLE` packet with blockers.

