>
> Its role is sharper: typed scientific kernels that emit compiler/runtime receipts.
>
> The megatool shape is:
>
> Gather sources -> Index context -> Forum lane -> BuildLang kernel -> Crucible verdict -> Learn receipt -> Telos packet.

