## Post 62: Climate Claims Need Receipts

> Climate AI is exactly where proof-carrying claims matter.
>
> Every public claim should name:
>
> data source, model version, forecast horizon, uncertainty, scenario boundary, and review status.
>
> Without those, the right verdict is not "AI says." It is `UNVERIFIABLE`.

Evidence: `docs/research/whitepapers/CROSS-DOMAIN-EXPERIMENT-ROUTERS-2026-07-02.md`

